<p>
  Thank you for choosing MortgageClub. Weâ€™re working hard to help close your loan on time!
</p>

<p>
  In order to meet estimated closing date of 11/23/16, please complete the items below no later than <%= @checklists.first.due_date.strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %>. Failure to complete these items by <%= @checklists.first.due_date.strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %> will delay your closing date. You can email these documents back to me or upload them in your Borrower Dashboard.
